Definition: lacking or showing a lack of what is fitting and considerate in dealing with others
Example: in the circumstances it was tactless to ask her age
Synonyms: noun, attribute, tactlessness, TACTFUL, untactful, INCONSIDERATE, INELEGANT, lacking, or, showing, a, lack, of, what, is, fitting, and, considerate, in, dealing, with, others, the, circumstances, it, was, tactless, to, ask, her, age
Category: adj.all
